On a normal headlamp, there is typically some residual drain as long as the battery is connected in the circuit, even when the light is off. With a simple pull on the front of the face, you can completely disengage your batteries, so they can be stored in your headlamp for years (up to their inherent shelf life). You’ll also reduce the toxic corrosion that can damage your headlamp. Using your headlamp is as easy as protecting it. Just slip on the fully-adjustable head strap and use the single-button to easily cycle through high, low and red modes. No matter the situation, from power outages to roadside emergencies, a headlamp with the BatteryLock system is ready, even when you arent.Coleman Divide+ 175L LED Headlamp

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
